    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I think you need to change the looping condition which is the problem here. You are looping one more iteration when you do <code>&lt;=size</code> and the index starts from <code>i=0</code>. You can change this </p>\n\n<pre><code>for(int i=0; i&lt;=size; i++)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>to</p>\n\n<pre><code>for(int i=0; i&lt;size; i++)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and also take care about the inner loop condition.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3104709,
      "reputation" : 35,
